{"tid":364863,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[無知]最近先知馬來西亞人原來有好多人種","createTime":"2017-08-18T17:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T10:33:45.000Z","uid":1249,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b4376376025c870ea5c005af316b8e38e338ec5","tid":364863,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T17:45:53.000Z","msg":"以前一直以為馬來西亞係窮版新加坡，大部分都係黃皮膚講蝗語嘅人，最近先知原來馬來西亞有分馬來人印度人原住民華人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係話大部分都唔係黃種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753146aa8a400e54a4b6a56ba5379e885555ed2b","tid":364863,"uid":62121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T17:55:06.000Z","msg":"我有個馬來西亞華人朋友話我聽<br />\n佢地一般唔多敢去啲傳統馬拉人（黑蚊蚊 又包頭）屋企<br />\n因為話佢地會落啲降頭落隻家貓道 摸一摸隻貓 就會中左貓降<br />\n<br />\n利 佢咁講 我咁聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff4091c00204e0ddfc9d0f2e01dd16b9115e82e","tid":364863,"uid":62020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T17:57:58.000Z","msg":"佢地啲華人同馬來人係完全唔同"},{"pid":"e6093d91694bd0e39523cf5c6d03f18c75588a6b","tid":364863,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T17:59:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d65446d1b1c9fd1944c877c084f801f4fe6fbba8","tid":364863,"uid":81546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T18:02:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d928de0c8dedc04535e0aed4be9db9f30e06d021","tid":364863,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T18:08:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩個世界既人（計埋印度佬就三個）住係同一撻地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：有親戚係大馬</blockquote><br />\n我真係最近先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"h